org.sakaiproject.tool.section.jsf.backingbean

Class PreferencesBean

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sakaiproject.tool.section.jsf.backingbean.InitializableBean
      • org.sakaiproject.tool.section.jsf.backingbean.CourseDependentBean
        • org.sakaiproject.tool.section.jsf.backingbean.PreferencesBean
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, PhaseAware

    public class PreferencesBean
extends CourseDependentBean
    Stores user preferences for table sorting and paging. These preferences are currently implemented in session-scope, though this could be reimplemented to store preferences across sessions.
    Author:
    Josh Holtzman
